metadata.name: Provenance
metadata.description: [Provenance] is the 1st piece of the [ze Luna] collection to be minted via the Manifold platform. It is a first for me to mint via a non-marketplace platform and serves as a signifier of the wonders of the Web3 space. The title pays homage to the platform's motto and vision and as a new exciting start for me as an artist. This is also the first special piece to have editions, since I have all along been creating 1/1 art. Cheers to all the hardworking artists and supportive collectors out there; and cheers to more great art in the world! Sincerely, Paper.
